 NVIM CHEATSHEET                              q to close

 WINDOWS (splits)
  Ctrl-w s        Split horizontal
  Ctrl-w v        Split vertical
  Ctrl-w h/j/k/l  Navigate between windows
  Ctrl-w q        Close window
  Ctrl-w o        Close all other windows
  Ctrl-w =        Equalise window sizes

 NAVIGATION
  h j k l        Left / down / up / right
  w  b           Next / previous word
  0  $           Start / end of line
  gg  G          Top / bottom of file
  Ctrl-d  Ctrl-u Half page down / up
  {  }           Previous / next paragraph
  f<char>         Find char forwards on line
  F<char>         Find char backwards on line
  ;  ,           Repeat last f/F same / opposite direction

 EDITING
  i  a           Insert before / after cursor
  o  O           New line below / above
  u  Ctrl-r      Undo / redo
  dd  yy         Delete / yank line
  p  P           Paste below / above
  ciw  diw       Change / delete inner word

 SEARCH
  /              Search forward
  n  N           Next / previous match
  *              Search word under cursor

 SNIPPETS (insert mode)
  <trigger>       Type trigger word (e.g. test, data, fun)
  Ctrl-Space      Pop completion menu (snippets show [Snip])
  CR              Accept / expand selected snippet
  Tab             Jump to next placeholder
  Shift-Tab       Jump to previous placeholder

 LSP
  gd             Go to definition
  gI             Go to implementation
  gr             Show references
  K              Hover documentation (type info)
  Space rn       Rename symbol
  Space ca       Code action
  Space f        Format file
  Space e        Show line diagnostics
  ]d  [d         Next / previous diagnostic
  Space fs       List symbols in file (methods/classes)
  Space fS       List symbols in workspace
  a Ctrl-Space   (insert mode) Trigger completion popup
                 e.g. after App(). to list methods

 FOLDING
  za             Toggle fold under cursor
  zo  zc         Open / close fold under cursor
  zO  zC         Open / close fold recursively
  zR  zM         Open / close all folds in file
  zi             Toggle foldenable on/off
  zj  zk         Jump to next / previous fold

 FILES & BUFFERS
  :w             Save
  :q  :q!        Quit / force quit
  :wq            Save and quit
  :e <file>      Open file
